Raymond Souplex https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Raymond_Souplex 0 Raymond Souplex (1 June 1901 – 22 November 1972) was a French actor and singer. He was in a long-term relationship with Jane Sourza, although they never married. Raymond_Souplex ( 1_June_1901 – 22_November_1972 ) was a_French_actor_and_singer .
